import React from 'react';
import { MDBTable, MDBTableHead, MDBTableBody } from 'mdb-react-ui-kit';

export default function Table() {
    return ( <
        MDBTable >
        <
        MDBTableHead >
        <
        tr >
        <
        th scope = 'col' > # < /th> <
        th scope = 'col' > First < /th> <
        th scope = 'col' > Last < /th> <
        th scope = 'col' > Handle < /th> < /
        tr > <
        /MDBTableHead> <
        MDBTableBody >
        <
        tr className = 'table-active' >
        <
        th scope = 'row' > 1 < /th> <
        td > Mark < /td> <
        td > Otto < /td> <
        td > @mdo < /td> < /
        tr > <
        tr >
        <
        th scope = 'row' > 2 < /th> <
        td > Jacob < /td> <
        td > Thornton < /td> <
        td > @fat < /td> < /
        tr > <
        tr >
        <
        th scope = 'row' > 3 < /th> <
        td colSpan = { 2 }
        className = 'table-active' >
        Larry the Bird <
        /td> <
        td > @twitter < /td> < /
        tr > <
        /MDBTableBody> < /
        MDBTable >
    );
}
